OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry, bright
OL,6,Fstart this evening but outbreaks of
OL,7,Fheavy thundery rain, risk of
OL,8,Ftorrential downpours and hail, edging
OL,9,Finto Moray, and across the region
OL,10,Fovernight. Drier later in west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA cloudy day with occasional
OL,13,Frain, some of this may be heavy and
OL,14,Fperhaps thundery at times. Some drier
OL,15,Fspells of weather too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
