OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FBright
OL,6,Fstart Saturday, some very warm
OL,7,Fsunshine for north coast, but cloud
OL,8,Fincreasing with showery rain later.
OL,9,FSunday and Monday see sunny spells and
OL,10,Fshowers, with a fresh southwesterly
OL,11,Fbreeze.
